---
const misreads = [
  { wrong: 'A reporting problem', right: 'mistaken for a CRM problem.' },
  { wrong: 'An operational problem', right: 'mistaken for an AI problem.' },
  { wrong: 'A business shaped by its software', right: 'instead of software shaped around the business.' },
];
---

<section class="section why" id="why">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split">
      <div class="split__aside">
        <p class="eyebrow coral reveal">Why It Matters</p>
        <h2 class="why__title reveal" data-delay="1">
          Most organizations don't have a technology problem.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="why__body">
        <div class="prose reveal">
          <p>
            Every week brings another AI announcement, another platform, another consultant explaining why
            you need to transform. The instinct is to ask <em>"what should we implement?"</em> — and that is
            the wrong question.
          </p>
          <p>
            Across three decades in global telecoms, enterprise software and non-profits, the same pattern
            repeats regardless of size or industry: a <strong>business problem</strong> being solved as if it
            were a technology one.
          </p>
        </div>

        <ul class="why__list reveal" data-delay="1">
          {misreads.map((m) => (
            <li>
              <span class="why__wrong">{m.wrong}</span>
              <span class="why__right">{m.right}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <figure class="why__quote reveal">
      <blockquote>
        Solve the wrong problem, and better software simply gets you to the wrong destination faster.
      </blockquote>
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why__title { font-size: var(--fs-h2); }
  .why__body { padding-top: 0.4rem; }
  .why__list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .why__list li {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.5rem 0.9rem;
    padding: 1.15rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .why__wrong {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-strong);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .why__right { color: var(--text-muted); }

  .why__quote {
    margin: clamp(3.5rem, 7vw, 6rem) auto 0;
    max-width: 36rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .why__quote blockquote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: var(--fs-quote);
    line-height: 1.18;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text-strong);
  }
  .why__quote blockquote::before { content: "“"; color: var(--coral); }
  .why__quote blockquote::after { content: "”"; color: var(--coral); }
</style>
